➜索尼向含有“Pixels”一字的视频大规模发出DMCA删除通知
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=45072	9889
<center>
<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/aUnyUrA34bQ" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" width="560"></iframe><br>
